                                <span class="info-title3">InvoiceName </span> :  Tên HÓA ĐƠN.<br>
                                <span class="info-title3">SerialNo </span> : Kí hiệu HÓA ĐƠN.<br>
                                <span class="info-title3">InvoicePattern </span> : Kí hiệu mẫu HÓA ĐƠN.<br>
                                <span class="info-title3">InvoiceNo </span> : Số HÓA ĐƠN.<br>
                                <span class="info-title3">KindofPayment</span> : Hình thức thanh toán.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-5">
                            <img class="img-responsive" src="/img/GENERAL-INFO.png" width="881" height="188">
                        </div>

                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item ">
                <div class="text-info" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#cautruc" href="#supplierinfo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="supplierinfo">
